exclaimed,
"To
treat
in
such
a
manner
the
godson,
the
friend,
the
favourite
of
his
father!"
She
could
have
added,
"A
young
man,
too,
like
you,
whose
very
countenance
may
vouch
for
your
being
amiable"
but
she
contented
