reverting
once
more
to
the
first,
and
saying:
"I
am
astonished
at
his
intimacy
with
Mr.
Bingley!
How
can
Mr.
Bingley,
who
seems
good
humour
itself,
and
is,
I
really
believe,
truly
amiable,
